        {
          "lang": "zh-TW",
          "lang_word": "impress",
          "definition": "vt. 使印象深刻、打動  vi. 給人留下印象"
        }
      ],
      "examples": [
        {
          "en": "The candidate tried to impress the interviewer with her fluency in three languages.",
